description.fr: De retour dans les galeries, {CharacterName:708} retrouve {CharacterName:474}, bien décidée à libérer la {Summoning:1354}.
description.en: Back in the tunnels, {CharacterName:708} has found {CharacterName:474}, determined to release the {Summoning:1354}.
description.es: De vuelta en las galerías, {CharacterName:708} encuentra a {CharacterName:474}, totalmente decidida a liberar a la {Summoning:1354}.
description.de: Zurück in den Tunneln findet {CharacterName:708} {CharacterName:474} wieder, die entschlossen ist, die {Summoning:1354} zu befreien.
description.pt: De volta às galerias, {CharacterName:708} reencontra {CharacterName:474}, decidida a libertar a {Summoning:1354}.

descriptionFinished.fr: La {Summoning:1354} se trouve bel et bien dans les galeries, mais {CharacterName:708} et {CharacterName:474} n'arrivent pas à s'en approcher. Il va falloir persévérer.
descriptionFinished.en: The {Summoning:1354} is indeed in the tunnels, but {CharacterName:708} and {CharacterName:474} haven't been able to get near her. Perseverance is needed.
descriptionFinished.es: La {Summoning:1354} se encuentra en efecto en las galerías, pero {CharacterName:708} y {CharacterName:474} no consiguen acercarse a ella. Habrá que perseverar.
descriptionFinished.de: Die {Summoning:1354} befindet sich tatsächlich in den Tunneln, {CharacterName:708} und {CharacterName:474} gelingt es jedoch nicht, in ihre Nähe zu gelangen. Sie müssen durchhalten.
descriptionFinished.pt: A {Summoning:1354} está nas galerias, mas {CharacterName:708} e {CharacterName:474} não conseguem encontrá-la. Eles deverão perseverar.
